{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"dfa6cb2b-092e-4d00-bf0d-0e633af30cf2","content":"Your `.testsettings` file contains three settings to migrate:\n\n| Setting | `.testsettings` | MSTest v3 equivalent |\n|---|---|---|\n| Test timeout | `<Property name=\"TestTimeout\" value=\"30000\" />` | `.runsettings` → `<TestTimeout>` |\n| Code coverage | `<DataCollector>` in `<AgentRule>` | `.runsettings` → `<DataCollectors>` |\n| Assembly resolution | `<AssemblyResolution>` | No longer needed (handled automatically) |\n\n`.testsettings` is **not supported** in MSTest v3. You replace it with a `.runsettings` file. Here's the migration:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01EEAgZh9X34uxm7s58TKnVA","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01EamnHgzRyyuuN6sydi7vUc","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-bafc77768a904753ba6e721b25def523/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <!-- Replaces <Property name=\"TestTimeout\" value=\"30000\" /> -->\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <!-- Replaces the code coverage DataCollector from .testsettings -->\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.CoverageCollectorDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral\" />\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-bafc77768a904753ba6e721b25def523/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"ca9d1865-55c0-4a97-9e47-71a271666ada","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file with:\n1. Assembly resolution / test deployment config\n2. A test timeout of 30000ms (30 seconds)\n3. 